  I am her man both day and nygth __
  And so wol be. Ther -- fore y wolde, as y love __ her,
  She lo -- vyd me. __
}

wordsOneC = \lyricmode {
  \set stanza = "3."

  Whan she is mery than am y gladde;
  Whan she is sory than am y sadde, __
  And cause is whye: For he le -- veth not that lo -- vyd
  So wel as y. __
}

